The paper discusses the state-of-the-art of IoT, its potential applications, challenges, and future research areas. It also compares IoT definitions from different perspectives in academic and industry communities. These topics are related to computer networks (cs.NI), cybersecurity (cs.CY), software engineering (cs.SE), distributed computing (cs.DC), and cryptography (cs.CR).
